DESCRIPTION:2026-03-29 14:00:00\n\nLocal H-110\, 1455 Maisonneuve W (metro
  Guy)\n\nhttps://www.openstreetmap.org/node/4035248248\n\nJulia Loktev doc
 uments independent journalists in Moscow facing government crackdown as Ru
 ssia invades Ukraine\, capturing their fight for speech amid risks of bein
 g branded “foreign agents” and the country’s drift towards authorita
 rianism.
